Given the following program and the variable in complex data type, decompose the it into variables with primary data type.. The program is char fn1(char p1, char p2) { return p1 * p2; }
struct g {
  int h;
};
int i;
struct g j;
int *fn2(unsigned p1, int *p2, char p3) {
  for (p3 = 6; p3 != -7; p3--)
    j.h ^= fn1(p3, i) && 1L;
  return p2;
}
int main() { return 0; }
.                 The target to be optimized is `p2`: This is a pointer variable that points to an `int` value..
